We have been ordering here for a while. We live in an area with a ton of Chinese restaurants but we keep coming back here. It’s the perfect Chinese takeout - delicious, inexpensive and fast.  The owner is super cool and speaks 3 languages - Spanish, English and Chinese. It’s a trip to see him taking multiple orders and switching between languages.  Note that it really is only for takeout - it’s a tiny place with no room for dine in. House of Changs is awesome - our go to Chinese joint.
